data.description: Nestled in a sought-after lake community with boat storage, this custom-built gem, crafted by a local builder on a cul-de-sac lot, is only 5 years old and quality-built with all the bells and whistles! Step into the luxury of a well-equipped home with an excellent floor plan. The gourmet kitchen even boasts a wine fridge, a stainless 5-burner gas stove & a microwave drawer. Many other conveniences throughout, including a tankless water heater. Outdoors you'll find a well-designed outdoor living space with a covered back porch, a patio with pergola, stacked-stone seating around the fire pit on the paver patio, and a private backyard. Enjoy watching the game while hanging out in the jacuzzi with a large fire to keep you warm while friends and pets hang out on the large outdoor couch swing! This residence caters to water enthusiasts with a public boat ramp nearby as the home is in a central Denver location. Differentiate yourself from the masses—this is not just a house; it's a lifestyle.
